      <title>调查发现瑞银行业客户越来越挑剔</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-industry-customers-increasingly-critical-survey-finds-2024-09-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查发现，自 2023 年瑞信收购瑞银以来，近四分之一的瑞士工业公司对瑞银的服务（尤其是在贷款方面）感到不满，这对瑞银试图表明其未滥用市场主导地位的努力造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-industry-customers-increasingly-critical-survey-finds-2024-09-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
